<ab facs="#facs_279_line_1576661746196_6924"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> niht ıſt vnd wır ſein niht mechtıg ſein vnd <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> niht . denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_line_1576661750460_6929">daʒ er <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Burggraf <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ſey . als wır eẅch das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l29">nehſt auch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Denn wo wır eẅch ſuſt lıeb </ab>
