<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hanns, als ir uns aber
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Ott Heydens
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Ott Heyden unser
                                <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> niht ist und wir sein niht mechtig
                        sein; und <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> niht denn, daz er
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> burggraf <expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> sey, als wir ewch das nehst auch
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Denn wo wir ewch sust lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Judica. </ab>
</div>
